# 🔐 Security Review: `app.js`

The file is a minimal Express.js server (22 lines). Despite its simplicity, it contains several real vulnerabilities and establishes dangerous patterns that will compound as the application grows. Below are findings mapped to OWASP Top 10 (2021), ordered by severity.

