  // use page/limit safely
});
```

---

#### 6. Hardcoded Data Will Become an Injection Point (OWASP A03)
The user list is currently static, but it will almost certainly be replaced with a database query. Constructing queries with unsanitized user input is the #1 injection vector.

**Fix — when you add a DB layer, always use parameterized queries:**

