## Detailed Findings

### 🔴 1. No Authentication on `/users` — Broken Access Control (A01)

**Problem:** The `/users` endpoint returns user data (including emails) to any unauthenticated caller. Anyone who can reach port 3000 gets the full user list.

```js
// ❌ Current — completely open
